These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, lily
1. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
2. the person who growslily is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | sprite   | 7up  |
| Sport   | iris | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, cricket
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, chestnut
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person who's sport is cricket##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | rugby | cricket      |
| Pet    | fuchsia  | chestnut |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, ship
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the havana-smoker is not the person driving the bus##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | ship  | bus    |
| Sport   | havana | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
