The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, march
1. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating onion is not the person who's birthday is in march##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | onion | avocado |
| Pet   | july       | march       |

